data.description:
Welcome to this charming country home located just outside of Checotah, OK.
This lovely, well maintained home is now available for sale and offers a peaceful country living experience on a spacious almost 3 acre property.
Convenience is key, as this property provides easy access to Hwy 69, making commuting a breeze. The location also offers proximity to Lake Eufaula with a boat ramp just 2.5 miles east or 3 miles south, perfect for water enthusiasts and fishing lovers.
This property boasts a variety of features that enhance its appeal. A brand new air compressor and a 10' lean-to are included in the 30x30 shop with electricity, providing ample space for hobbies or storage needs.
Additionally, there is a convenient 26x32 RV carport for those who enjoy traveling in their recreational vehicles, or need a spot to store their boat! Bonus: 30 Amp plug in shop for that camper!
Inside the house, you'll find a bright clean space with new paint and laminate flooring. The kitchen comes equiped with all appliances, making meal prep a breeze. TV's and surround sound stay too, for your entertainment pleasure. The Trane AC and Heating unit is less than a year old, double pane windows throughout, and the Heritage roof still has 15 years left on it, making this home low maintenance and worry free!
Sit out on the covered back patio and enjoy your evenings with it's gorgeous acreage, convenient location, and desirable amenties. This property offers an ideal opportunity for those seeking a quiet lifestyle while still being close to town.
Don't miss out on the chance to make this your new home!
This immaculate home is being sold “As is”
